Introduction

Yujun is a South Korean singer under KQ Entertainment. He made his official debut on March 30, 2023, as one of the vocalists of the boy group xikers.

On August 20, 2022, he was introduced as the fifth member of KQ Fellaz 2.

On February 24, 2023, KQ announced that KQ Fellaz 2 would debut under the name xikers along with the help of the launching of social media and identity film for the group. They debuted on March 30, 2023, with their first mini album, "House of Tricky: Doorbell Ringing"
